{"title":"七十咏怀","authors":["丁力"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":5,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十咏怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七十如今不算稀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生百岁正相宜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气功勤练能增寿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好尽辛劳为众黎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难岁月易蹉跎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇事达观快乐多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历几番坎坷路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老来有劲战癌魔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼爱民歌少爱诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年始解拜良师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民间疾苦曾经受，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘流亡道上驰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七学诗今七十，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年月月不离诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛棚受审耕田日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要暗吟人不知。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素信写诗无秘诀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好诗多自生活掘；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭情作魂情要真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以意为主意应切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提倡国风民族风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不从古怪轻朦胧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年论诗归乡土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立意创新道路通。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}